cast.overview: After his impetuous musician girlfriend, Samantha, dies in an accident shortly after they had a fight (and nearly broke up), Ian Wyndham, a grief-stricken British businessman living in London gets a chance to relive the day all over again, in the hope of changing the events that led up to her getting killed.
cast.title: If Only

details.biography:
Jessica grew up in London and won a place at RADA aged 18 where she trained for three years. Throughout her teenage years she trained at The National Youth Theatre of Great Britain. She lives in London.

She has worked extensively for the BBC and is also known as a voice over work. She is best known for playing Vikki Du French in Pennyworth.
details.name: Jessica Claire
